# MathCoaster Project Rules

## Language in Code

**Use only English in code and in code literals.**

- Variable names, function names, class names → English
- String literals in code → English
- Comments in code → English
- Error messages, logs, UI text in source → English
- File names for source code → English

```typescript
// ❌ BAD
const имяПользователя = "Пользователь";
throw new Error("Ошибка загрузки");

// ✅ GOOD
const userName = "User";
throw new Error("Load error");
```

**Exception:** User-facing localization (i18n) strings for the application UI may use translated text and should be kept in locale files, not hardcoded.
